Title: An Act Changing the Name of Baybay Elementary School in the Municipality of Makato, Province of Aklan, to Col. Jose Tando Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 809
An Act Changing the Name of Baybay Elementary School in the Municipality of Makato, Province of Aklan, to Col. Jose Tando Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Baybay Elementary School located in Barangay Baybay in the Municipality of Makato, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Col. Jose Tando Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1avvphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
